stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initiated

    note right of Initiated: Application Start

    Initiated --> KYC: verify identity
    KYC --> BureauPull: pull credit
    BureauPull --> IncomeVerification: check income
    IncomeVerification --> RiskScoring: calculate score

    RiskScoring --> Decision

    Decision --> Approved: ≥ 750
    Decision --> ManualReview: 600-749
    Decision --> Rejected: < 600

    ManualReview --> Approved: approved
    ManualReview --> Rejected: rejected

    Approved --> [*]
    Rejected --> [*]

    note left of Approved: Auto or Manual
    note left of Rejected: Auto or Manual
